Create a URI with the given scheme specific part, local name, and fragment identifier.

Parameters:
scheme - The scheme for the URI, or null to be left undefined.
ssp - The scheme specific part for the URI, or null to be left undefined.
fragment - The fragment identifier, or null to be left undefined.
Returns:
A new URI according to the parameter values.
